<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Proposal Approved</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
      margin: auto;
      padding: 20px;
      max-width: 600px;
      background-color: #fff;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: right;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Proposal Approved</h1>
    <p>
      Dear {{username}},
    </p>
    <p>
      We are pleased to inform you that your proposal has been approved by the admin team. Congratulations!
    </p>
    <p>
      Here are the details of your approved proposal:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Title:</strong> {{proposalTitle}}</li>
      <li><strong>Description:</strong> {{proposalDescription}}</li>
      <li><strong>Approval Date:</strong> {{approvalDate}}</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      If you have any questions or need further assistance, please feel free to contact us. We look forward to seeing your proposal come to life.
    </p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>The Admin Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
